When you want to optimize the size, you're right, you'll need to define a `.bi` class somehow too because it's contained only in https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css.

If you're embedding the icons into a font, you could use the same rule as defined in https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css:

```css
.bi::before,
[class^="bi-"]::before,
