  text-transform: none;
  line-height: 1;
  vertical-align: -.125em;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
}
```

If you don't use a font to group together the icons but use them just as SVGs you could also use a `.bi` class that you need to add to your project with the following content (this is the rule we use in our examples in Bootstrap documentation):

```css
.bi {
